---

### 3. Katkı Kuralları İçin `CONTRIBUTING.md`
Açık kaynak puanını garantilemek için bu dosyayı da repoya ekle.

```markdown
# Contributing to Smart Patient Monitoring System

We welcome contributions to improve the RTOS simulation or the OpenCV fall detection algorithm!

## How to Contribute
1. Fork this repository.
2. Create a new branch: `git checkout -b feature/your-feature-name`.
3. Make your changes and test the `simpy` task schedulers to ensure no deadlocks occur.
4. Commit your changes: `git commit -m 'Add some feature'`.
5. Push to the branch: `git push origin feature/your-feature-name`.
6. Submit a pull request.

## Guidelines
- Ensure that any new RTOS task specifies its period, WCET (Worst Case Execution Time), and priority in the comments.
- Maintain the Python PEP-8 coding standards.
- If you add new models (like Synchronous Data Flow), please update the `README.md` documentation accordingly.
